title: Leasing Services
posting_body: Do you need to rent your house?
I am NOT offering management services, but I can help you get your house, condo or studio rented.
I will do the market survey to get a comparable data to set a realistic rental price for your Property.
I will do the background check and application process.
I will complete the lease agreement and move in inspection.
I will also be available to do the tours to the property.
I will give you all documents and moneys paid the day of the move in inspection.
My commission will be half of first months rent, one time fee and one time service.
